<body><page page_number="1" transcanno_page_id="2252"><paragraph class="medium-paragraph" tagcode="1610622246599"><div>ich denke, dass man Deutsch, <orth_error_id12 class="medium-orth_error_id12" orth_error_target="Italienisch" tagcode="1537930944883">Italienis</orth_error_id12> und <tran_word_deletion_id8 class="medium-tran_word_deletion_id8" tagcode="1537930948992" tran_word_deletion_target="_#_">en</tran_word_deletion_id8> <orth_error_id12 class="medium-orth_error_id12" orth_error_target="Englisch" tagcode="1537930962537">English</orth_error_id12></div><div>wissen sollte, weil es die wichtigsten Sprachen sind, vielleicht</div><div>eine Sprache noch in der Mittelschule lernen <tran_symbol_id32 class="medium-tran_symbol_id32" tagcode="1537930982386" tran_symbol_target="*">*</tran_symbol_id32></div><div>Und deshalb <tran_word_deletion_id8 class="medium-tran_word_deletion_id8" tagcode="1537930994384" tran_word_deletion_target="_#_">lernt in</tran_word_deletion_id8> <tran_word_insertion_id9 class="medium-tran_word_insertion_id9" tagcode="1537930998183">kann</tran_word_insertion_id9> <tran_word_deletion_id8 class="medium-tran_word_deletion_id8" tagcode="1537931002400" tran_word_deletion_target="_#_">lernt</tran_word_deletion_id8> man in den Oberschulen</div><div>auch andere lernen aber wir lernen diese 3 Sprachen</div><div>früher weil sie <tran_word_deletion_id8 class="medium-tran_word_deletion_id8" tagcode="1537931009887" tran_word_deletion_target="_#_">wichtiger</tran_word_deletion_id8> <tran_word_deletion_id8 class="medium-tran_word_deletion_id8" tagcode="1537931014288" tran_word_deletion_target="_#_">sind</tran_word_deletion_id8><tran_word_deletion_id8 class="medium-tran_word_deletion_id8" tagcode="1610622246598" tran_word_deletion_target="_#_">.</tran_word_deletion_id8> die mehrgesprochene</div><div>Sprachen sind</div></paragraph><paragraph class="medium-paragraph" tagcode="1610622246600"><div>Z.B. Spanisch.</div></paragraph><paragraph class="medium-paragraph" tagcode="1610622246601"><div>Italienisch spricht man nicht viel auf der Welt viel</div><div>aber wir lernen es in der Schule, weil wir</div><div>in Italien leben und wenn wir in Italien leben dann</div><div>müssten wir auch Italienisch wissen.</div></paragraph></page></body>
